<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你最近有要去找<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我跟<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
借了個東西，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但老是沒時間還給<gender3 m="他" f="她" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很信任你所以才這麼說，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以拜託你代替我
把東西還回去嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好呀！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />抱歉，我也沒空</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說前陣子<delay20 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay20 />
把東西放在我家忘了帶走啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是我馬上發現就好了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但等我發現，那傢伙早就回去不知道多久啦。<pageBreak />雖然照理說，由我送去給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />就行了，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我老是有別的事要忙，<delay8 />
事情就這樣擱著了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一直掛念著這件事，<delay20 />
覺得惱人得很啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />我幫你拿過去吧？</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />辛苦你了</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay20 />你聽我說……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子，<delay8 />有個要給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的包裹<delay8 />
誤送到我這裡來啦！
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正打算要打開時，
碰巧發現不對勁，<delay8 />才沒出什麼問題，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但總覺得很尷尬啊<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以不好意思，<delay8 />
你能幫我把這件包裹<delay20 />
拿去給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我知道了！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />抱歉，我也沒空</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />謝啦！<delay20 />
我果然沒有看錯你啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那這個<delay20 />就拜託你囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的嗎！？<delay20 />真是幫了我大忙……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是這個包裹了，<delay8 />
麻煩你囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你！<delay frames="40" />
這種事情啊，<delay8 />
我覺得還是要有個中間人<delay8 />會比較好。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那這個包裹<delay20 />
就麻煩你囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是嗎～<delay frames="30" />
抱歉，對你提出這種強人所難的要求。<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之後<delay8 />再親自還給對方吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是說啊～<delay frames="40" />
害我在意得不得了，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我就盡快拿去還給對方吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊……<delay20 />沒事，我才該跟你道歉。<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然包裝的邊緣<delay8 />已經有點翹起來了，<delay20 />
但我晚點還是親自還給對方吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="30" />
你來得正好！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實……<delay8 />我有點事想拜託你啊。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想要<delay20 />送禮物給<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />平常很照顧我的
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />我不知道
這種時候該怎麼面對<gender3 m="他" f="她" />啦～<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以拜託你！<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能請你幫我<delay20 />把這份禮物<delay8 />
交給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />嗎！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這種事就交給我吧！</message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />我會為你加油的！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你現在<delay20 />有空聽我說點話嗎？<pageBreak />其實我跟<delay20 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />吵了一架<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想要主動跟<gender3 m="他" f="她" />和好，<delay8 />
所以準備了賠罪時要送的禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我又不好意思當面交給<gender3 m="他" f="她" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
你能替我<delay8 />轉交給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這種事就交給我吧！</message>
	<message label="102_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">還是自己加油比較好吧</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是可靠！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
那這件禮物<delay20 />
就麻煩你囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你，<delay20 />我欠你一筆人情！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想給對方的是這個東西，<delay frames="40" />
那就麻煩你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊……<delay20 />果然是這樣嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我真的不好意思拿給對方啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" />既然如此，<delay20 />
我要不要乾脆喬裝一下再交給對方<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會努力<delay8 />想辦法的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說的也是啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
果然還是應該親自交給人家啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
謝謝你聽我說這些！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這讓我稍微提起一點勇氣了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">事不宜遲，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就麻煩你今天內送給對方囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今天已經很晚了，<delay8 />
所以你明天再拿給對方也沒關係。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就拜託你了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">剛才交給你的那個東西<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是要還給<delay8 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的喔。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就拜託你了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />也會<delay8 />忘記帶走東西，
真是個迷糊蛋呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思麻煩到你，<delay20 />
但是請替我拿給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這次<delay20 />一定要把包裹<delay8 />
好好交給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />喔。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />麻煩你囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我交給你的，
不僅僅是件禮物，<delay20 />還代表著我的心意。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你一定要<delay8 />
把我的心意<delay20 />確實交給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />麻煩你囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我把我的誠意交給你了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
你一定要<delay8 />送去給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這次全靠你啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
